{"tid":1374731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為證藥粉安全假醫師試食一口 怎知中毒身亡","createTime":"2019-07-28T00:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T04:12:36.000Z","uid":89046,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2c2dbd3775349e03d104811b745f8e001628ce38","tid":1374731,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T00:21:53.000Z","msg":"【為證藥粉安全假醫師試食一口】<br />\n【怎知中毒身亡】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=471892293371931&amp;id=265944843550009\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D471892293371931%26id%3D265944843550009&d=ajJRCbjZ3CJF8zdY8%2Fu%2F12vf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=68ec0d97\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=471892293371931&amp;id=265944843550009</a><br />\n<br />\n韶關礤下村的肖阿姨上星期因為腰痛，在村內一間理療中心求醫，怎知服藥後昏迷入院。醫生指她多器官功能損害，比如腎功能。<br />\n<br />\n肖阿姨說她去了一間專治骨科病的理療中心，在「醫師」游說下飲了他的藥「黑老虎」。豈料她服食半小時後就出事。她老公見勢色不對，背著她去找那位醫師，但鄒醫師卻信心滿滿，在他們面前吃了一勺藥粉。但他很快就感到不妥，隨即送院急救，最後更不治身亡。<br />\n<br />\n原來他服食的「黑老虎」藥粉，每公斤含有200毫克鈎吻素子。鈎吻素子來源於斷腸草，是一種有毒植物。<br />\n<br />\n為何鄒醫師吃了毒藥都不知？村民指他其實是無牌行醫。<br />\n<br />\n#斷腸草<br />\n#毒藥<br />\n#無料就唔好行醫<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eab5965ce7a4c945003d3795679bc5aaf2783bc9","tid":1374731,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T00:27:12.000Z","msg":"又會搵到毒品來賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca6f088a90badd46e36c2b148196b6fdd3a0fc7","tid":1374731,"uid":11254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T00:29:47.000Z","msg":"佢中情花毒？ 要食斷腸草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aea3b7e6d0aada5ae5c7237371bcadc2f0b466e9","tid":1374731,"uid":197640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c2dbd3775349e03d104811b745f8e001628ce38","tid":1374731,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20